ZH: 我把他们当成我自己的孩子一样宠爱。
EN: I treat them with the same kindness as my own children.

ZH: 她的父母已经把她宠坏了。
EN: Her parents have spoiled her.

ZH: 我对小狗宠爱有加。
EN: I dote on my puppy.

ZH: 她的男朋友对她非常宠爱。
EN: Her boyfriend spoils her rotten.

ZH: 他的母亲总是宠着他。
EN: His mother always indulges him.

ZH: 她宠溺着她的小猫。
EN: She coddles her kitten.

ZH: 他对她是一片宠爱。
EN: He showers her with affection.

ZH: 她是家里的公主，被所有人宠着。
EN: She is the princess of the family, pampered by everyone.

ZH: 这只小狗被主人宠坏了。
EN: This puppy has been spoiled by its owner.

