EN: Her husband spoils her.

ZH: 父母总是怕宠坏孩子。
EN: Parents are always afraid of spoiling their children.

ZH: 她承受不了被宠爱的感觉。
EN: She can't stand being spoilt.

ZH: 这位明星被粉丝们宠坏了。
EN: This celebrity has been spoiled by his fans.

ZH: 他喜欢宠溺着他的女儿。
EN: He enjoys pampering his daughter.

ZH: 这只小猫在被宠坏之后变得非常任性。
EN: This kitten became very spoiled and whiny.

